      "content": "i’ve been sitting here in this cafe in prague for like two hours just watching people pass by. i finally made it to all the places i put on my bucket list over the years... but now that i'm actually here, it just feels like i've seen all there is to see. like i've completed the itinerary and there aren't any more stops left that actually matter. it's just... empty.",
