    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i guess. it just feels like i've reached the end of the map, you know? like the credits are starting to roll on this whole trip. i look at these beautiful old streets and i don't feel any connection to them anymore. it's more like i'm just waiting for the train to take me back to a place that doesn't exist. i feel like i've finished the tour and there's nothing left to check off. i'm just... done with the itinerary.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
